Class Summary
Class Description
AutoCloseables Utility methods for adapting java.sql.* types to instances that implement AutoCloseable.
AutoCloseArray An AutoCloseable Array.
AutoCloseBlob An AutoCloseable Blob.
AutoCloseCallableStatement An AutoCloseable CallableStatement.
AutoCloseClob An AutoCloseable Clob.
AutoCloseConnection An AutoCloseable Connection to a database.
AutoCloseDataSource Wraps a DataSource so that it provides AutoCloseable Connection instances from the AutoCloseDataSource.getConnection() and AutoCloseDataSource.getConnection(String, String) methods.
AutoCloseDriver Wraps a Driver so that it provides AutoCloseable Connection instances from the AutoCloseDriver.connect(String, Properties) method.
AutoCloseDriverManager Utility similar to DriverManager for returning AutoCloseable connections from the DriverManager.
AutoCloseNClob An AutoCloseable NClob.
AutoClosePooledConnection An AutoCloseable PooledConnection.
AutoClosePreparedStatement An AutoCloseable PreparedStatement.
AutoCloseResultSet An AutoCloseable ResultSet.
AutoCloseSQLInput A SQLInput that provides AutoCloseable instances of Array, Blob, Clob, NClob, and SQLXML
AutoCloseSQLXML An AutoCloseable SQLXML.
AutoCloseStatement An AutoCloseable Statement.
